@startuml comunicacao-UC04
title VetCare+ - Diagrama de Comunicacao UC-04: Agendar Consulta

object "Tutor" as Tutor <<actor>>
object "SPA React" as UI
object "AuthFilter" as Auth
object "ConsultaController" as Ctrl
object "ConsultaService" as Svc
object "VeterinarioRepo" as VetRepo
object "ConsultaRepo" as ConsRepo
object "RabbitMQ" as MQ
object "NotificacaoWorker" as Notif

Tutor --> UI : 1: preencher e enviar
UI --> Auth : 2: POST /api/consultas (JWT)
Auth --> Ctrl : 3: validarToken e repassar
Ctrl --> Svc : 4: agendar(dto)
Svc --> VetRepo : 5: buscarPorId(vetId)
VetRepo --> Svc : 5.1: Veterinario
Svc --> ConsRepo : 6: existeConflito(vetId, dataHora)
ConsRepo --> Svc : 6.1: false
Svc --> ConsRepo : 7: salvar(Consulta)
ConsRepo --> Svc : 7.1: consulta(id)
Svc --> MQ : 8: publicar(ConsultaAgendadaEvent)
MQ --> Notif : 9: consumir evento
Notif --> Notif : 9.1: enfileirar lembrete 24h
Svc --> Ctrl : 10: ConsultaDTO
Ctrl --> UI : 11: 201 Created
UI --> Tutor : 12: confirmacao na tela

note bottom
  Fluxo resumido:
  1-3. Tutor envia, sistema autentica.
  4-6. Controller delega; service valida conflito (RN-01).
  7-8. Persiste consulta e publica evento de dominio.
  9. Worker assincrono agenda lembrete.
  10-12. Resposta volta ao tutor.
end note

@enduml
